          "type": "narration",
          "role": "narrator",
          "text": {
            "en": "Trapped under Mughal watch in faraway Agra, Shivaji waits in silence, planning every breath. One calm, daring night, he vanishes in disguise, carrying the dream of Swaraj back to the Deccan.",
